metadata.name: Pray for Ukraine
metadata.description:
We were attacked today.. 24.02.2022
This day will write down in history forever!

I minting this NFT at my grandmother house hiding from explosions with my kids 5 years old and only 1 week old my little daughter and my lovely wife who gave me these priceless treasures..

I can hear the bombing around the city... my hometown Sumy...

Me with my wife took this portrait back in 2014 and never could have imagined that something like this could happen that we are experiencing nowâ€¦

Support each other
We are human beings and we want world peace

Pray for Ukraine..
